# Load Libraries
```{r}
library(DataExplorer)
library(tidyverse)
library(here)
```

# Read In Data
```{r}
stars <- read_csv(here("Week_10", "Data", "stars.csv"))
chem <- read_csv(here("Week_7", "Data", "chemicaldata_maunalua.csv"))
```

# Making Plots
```{r}
plot_histogram(chem)
plot_density(chem)
```
